
		     Apple Emulator Joystick Documentation



	Keystroke			Description
	---------		-------------------------


	NumLock 		Toggle between keyboard and joystick mode

	Shift+NumLock		Toggle joystick between analog/binary type

	Ctrl+NumLock		Toggle between normal/flight mode

	Alt+NumLock		Toggle between normal/self-center mode

	Ctrl+Alt+NumLock	Toggle between normal/fast response mode

	Ctrl+Alt+Shift+NumLock	Reset joystick to default (Binary normal)

	Alt+Ins 		Increase X axis center position (Medium inc.)

	Alt+Del 		Decrease X axis center position (Medium dec.)

	Alt+Shift+Ins		Increase X axis center position (Small inc.)

	Alt+Shift+Del		Decrease X axis center position (Small dec.)

	Ctrl+Ins		Increase X axis resolution (Medium increment)

	Ctrl+Del		Decrease X axis resolution (Medium decrement)

	Ctrl+Shift+Ins		Increase X axis resolution (Small increment)

	Ctrl+Shift+Del		Decrease X axis resolution (Small decrement)

	Alt+Pad_Plus		Increase Y axis center position (Medium inc.)

	Alt+Pad_Minus		Decrease Y axis center position (Medium dec.)

	Alt+Shift+Pad_Plus	Increase Y axis center position (Small inc.)

	Alt+Shift+Pad_Minus	Decrease Y axis center position (Small dec.)

	Ctrl+Pad_Plus		Increase Y axis resolution (Medium increment)

	Ctrl+Pad_Minus		Decrease Y axis resolution (Medium decrement)

	Ctrl+Shift+Pad_Plus	Increase Y axis resolution (Small increment)

	Ctrl+Shift+Pad_Minus	Decrease Y axis resolution (Small decrement)

	Tab			Fire button 1

	Alt			Fire button 2

